<section id="home">
    <h2>Home - Nagpur</h2>
    <p>Nagpur is a beautiful city located in Maharashtra and is known as the Orange City of India. It is centrally located and well connected by road, rail, and air. From Nagpur, travelers can easily plan a journey to northern destinations like Kashmir.</p>
</section>

<section id="destination">
    <h2>Destination - Kashmir</h2>
    <p>Kashmir is one of the most beautiful destinations in India. Known as "Paradise on Earth", it is famous for snow-covered mountains, valleys, Dal Lake, Mughal gardens, and wooden houseboats. Popular tourist places include Srinagar, Gulmarg, Pahalgam, and Sonmarg.</p>
</section>

