<section id="about">
    <h2>About Kashmir</h2>
    <p>Kashmir is located in the northern part of India. It is known for its breathtaking natural beauty, pleasant climate, traditional handicrafts, Kashmiri shawls, and delicious cuisine like Rogan Josh and Kahwa tea. Tourists enjoy shikara rides on Dal Lake, trekking in the mountains, skiing in Gulmarg, and exploring scenic valleys.</p>
</section>

